contentrichtext.text: {{Italic title prefixed|3}} '''USS ''Dixie''''' has been the name of more than one United States Navy ship, and may refer to: * {{USS|Dixie|1893}}, a ship in commission as an auxiliary cruiser from 1898 to 1899, as a training ship from 1899 to 1902, as a transport from 1903 to 1905 and from 1906 to 1907, and as a destroyer tender from 1909 to 1922 * {{USS|Dixie|AD-14}}, a destroyer tender in commission from 1940 to 1982 It may also refer to: *{{USS|Dixie III|SP-701}}, later USS ''SP-701'', a patrol boat in commission from 1917 to 1919 {{Shipindex}} {{DEFAULTSORT:Dixie}} [[Category:United States Navy ship names]]
